{"tid":1049631,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"［集思廣益］請假去面試","createTime":"2019-03-06T11:59:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-07T23:37:09.000Z","uid":124466,"like":14,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"7cb6f7e0a84dc7d637e4a199a39eb526222c67df","tid":1049631,"uid":124466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T11:59:30.000Z","msg":"是咁的，小弟做緊依家份工未夠一年，因為想搵份人工高d既工，一直都有報出面既工，最近收到面試通知，暫定下星期三，但好衰唔衰我因為之前請病假請得密（唔係病到番唔到既，有時係訓唔醒想射波） ，被我呀頭照肺，話公司culture唔鼓勵同事請咁多病假，同埋之前有同事發燒都照番工，暗裡想警告我唔好請咁多病假。<br />\n<br />\n咁我原本打算下星期個面試都諗住請病假去in，但依家咁被佢暗串，我又淆淆地，有冇巴絲有好提議，或者你地用過咩理由去請假見工？<br />\n<br />\n利申：SL 仲有一日Quota, AL負緊（公司要做夠一年先俾年假）"},{"pid":"9f0f81212f472cf6b96ced60ca4db94fe52d164a","tid":1049631,"uid":59848,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T12:02:18.000Z","msg":"請no pay leave話屋企有事<br />\n咁都唔比咁呢間嘢唔做都罷<br />\nbtw 請病假有醫生紙佢咬你食呀？洗怕佢"},{"pid":"a83171774ed4e521eb103fde87e5b8fa6bbbd436","tid":1049631,"uid":224107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T12:02:51.000Z","msg":"射波<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92a38cea16d2e9809aedf4ef181f6fdf671b4c34","tid":1049631,"uid":37746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T12:07:47.000Z","msg":"事假啦 唔好理佢批唔批 手腳係你度 唔由得佢控制你"},{"pid":"265c8d8ed7f5faec2aeaef66a2766fbbbf27cfce","tid":1049631,"uid":43557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T12:09:11.000Z","msg":"洗閪驚佢咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb155d2c65d0144c866efce6451ffa62251df1b5","tid":1049631,"uid":138522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T12:12:44.000Z","msg":"家有要事請假一天"},{"pid":"7d9ebd5cc82681ac9847a307400211cfdc2359e5","tid":1049631,"uid":18569,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T12:12:56.000Z","msg":"男人老狗咁細膽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class